    {
      "id": "PopularPost367979",
      "post_content": "Obviously each playgroup will have their own terms, but as a person that has been playing since Mirage, \"ping\" is the term I have heard most when dealing 1 dmg to a target. [Prodigal Sorcerer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prodigal Sorcerer), aka \"Tim\" (Monty Python's Holy Grail reference for those wondering), being the original \"pinger\". Not saying \"poke\" is wrong, per se, but I am sure more MTG players would understand/use \"ping\". With that being said, I wouldn't consider this card's ability a \"ping\" ability. It cannot tap to deal 1 dmg, but rather deals 1 dmg when it is declared as an attacker. ",
      "posted_by": "Bbone37",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost367979\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">Obviously each playgroup will have their own terms, but as a person that has been playing since Mirage, \"ping\" is the term I have heard most when dealing 1 dmg to a target. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Prodigal Sorcerer\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prodigal Sorcerer\">Prodigal Sorcerer</a>, aka \"Tim\" (Monty Python's Holy Grail reference for those wondering), being the original \"pinger\". Not saying \"poke\" is wrong, per se, but I am sure more MTG players would understand/use \"ping\". With that being said, I wouldn't consider this card's ability a \"ping\" ability. It cannot tap to deal 1 dmg, but rather deals 1 dmg when it is declared as an attacker. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '367979'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy99869\">Bbone37</span>\r\n                                (3/18/2014 11:47:48 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent